  "text": "2) What is the most effective biological dosing scheme for EGFR TKIs? Most current EGFR TKIs are used at their maximum tolerated dose in a daily dosing fashion (67). However, innovative preclinical modeling studies have demonstrated that combinations of less-toxic dosing schemes with intermittent pulsatile dosing periods may be a more rational treatment approach [CITATION_1] . Clinical trials using alternative dosing schemes are under way.",
